<title>
Input Shaft Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206015">Manual Transaxle Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206018">Input Shaft Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5206019001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
Supporting the gear on the concave side of the puller can cause damage to the gear.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Be sure to support the gear on the flat side of the puller.
</ptxt>
</attention4>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove circlip (1) using special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B022">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09900-06107">
09900–06107
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520038.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.056mm" ver = "01" gw = "81" gh = "125"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove input shaft right bearing (2) and left bearing (4) from input shaft (1) using bearing puller (3) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520041.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.187mm" ver = "02" gw = "167" gh = "106"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.326in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
5.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Metal stick
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove 6th gear spacer (1) and 6th gear (2) from input shaft (4) using bearing puller (3) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520042.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "54.423mm" ver = "01" gw = "156" gh = "138"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove 5th and 6th synchronizer sleeve &#38; hub assembly (1) and 5th gear (2) using bearing puller (3) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520043.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.837mm" ver = "01" gw = "138" gh = "122"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove 5th gear needle bearing from input shaft.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove 5th gear spacer according to the following procedure.
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Engage high speed synchronizer sleeve to 4th gear.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Push down input shaft (1) a little using bearing puller (2) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520039.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "75.029mm" ver = "01" gw = "185" gh = "196"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove 5th gear spacer (1) using bearing puller (2) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520040.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "60.304mm" ver = "01" gw = "185" gh = "154"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove 4th gear, 4th gear synchronizer ring and 4th gear needle bearing from input shaft.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove circlip (1) using special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B023">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09900-06107">
09900–06107
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520041.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "67.848mm" ver = "01" gw = "143" gh = "176"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove high speed synchronizer sleeve &#38; hub assembly (1) and 3rd gear (2) from input shaft (4) using bearing puller (3) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520042.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "70.214mm" ver = "03" gw = "185" gh = "183"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove 3rd gear needle bearing from input shaft.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disassemble synchronizer sleeve &#38; hub assembly.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5206019002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206020">Input Shaft Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206027">Gear Shift Shaft and Fork Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install right bearing (1) to input shaft (2) using special tool and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B024">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09941-74910">
09941–74910
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520048.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "62.089mm" ver = "01" gw = "115" gh = "159"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Fit high speed synchronizer sleeve (1) to hub (2) and 3 keys (3) as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
No specific direction is assigned to each key but it is assigned as sleeve &#38; hub assembly.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Inside diameter of high speed synchronizer hub is larger than that of low speed synchronizer hub.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<title>
Synchronizer key installation position
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP70A520008.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "79.111mm" ver = "01" gw = "153" gh = "208"/>
<callout>
