Key way
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install 3rd gear needle bearing (4) and apply transaxle oil to it, and then install 3rd gear synchronizer ring (2) and 3rd gear (1) to input shaft.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install high speed sleeve &#38; hub assembly (3) using special tool and hydraulic press and then install circlip.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
While press-fitting sleeve &#38; hub, make sure that synchronizer ring key protrusion (5) are aligned with keys in sleeve &#38; hub assembly.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check free rotation of 3rd gear after press-fitting sleeve &#38; hub assembly.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<c-change/>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B025">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09944-77030">
09944–77030
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP70A520005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "97.739mm" ver = "02" gw = "170" gh = "261"/>
<callout>
