<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install 4th gear needle bearing (2) and apply transaxle oil to it, and then install synchronizer ring (4) and 4th gear (3).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install 5th gear spacer (1) using special tools and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Using an inappropriate hydraulic press or bearing puller could cause personal injury.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Make sure that both the hydraulic press and bearing puller are capable of safely bearing a load of at least 5 tons (11,000 lbs).
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B026">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09940-54910">
09940–54910
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B027">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-85210">
09913–85210
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520066.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "54.010mm" ver = "01" gw = "88" gh = "137"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install 5th gear needle bearing and apply transaxle oil to it, and then install 5th gear and synchronizer ring.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Fit 5th &#38; 6th gear synchronizer sleeve (1) to hub (2) and 3 keys (3) as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
No specific direction is assigned to 5th &#38; 6th gear synchronizer hub or each key but it is assigned as assembly.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Inside diameter at 5th &#38; 6th gear synchronizer hub is smaller than that of low speed synchronizer hub.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<title>
Synchronizer key installation position
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP70A520009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "74.208mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "194"/>
